AppName

Provide a human readable app name. The name will show when interoperating with other Jabra.NET.Sdk applications and services. One example is the preferred softphone selector in Jabra.NET.Sdk Direct.

Declaration
public string AppName { get; }
Property Value
Type Description
System.String
Remarks

Must begin with a ASCII letter or number. There is a 100 characters length limit. It can contain ASCII letters, numbers, dashes and underscores.
